Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:15.30,Staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片源\Nchiwa\N\N\N　壓製\N　xelnaga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.24,0:01:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#09 黑暗深處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣\N最初兩人認識的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老師和學生的關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像全班都發了喜帖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻來不到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是誰，根本想不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堇川妳以前常常缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在寫小說\N白白浪費了青春時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有交男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，妳有女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是其他老師請產假時\N那個戴眼鏡的代課老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，她啊\N叫什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀子．利德曼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有那種興趣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是辭掉學校工作後\N她一直住在妳那裡不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念喔，她現在在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行蹤不明，已經四年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不知道晃到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來妳一直沒有寫書\N就是因為這個原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不只是這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝完喜酒後\N我們三個去泡溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是附近有發現\N遺跡的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，對啊\N有古代人墳墓的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家以熱烈的掌聲\N歡迎新人進場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來啦\N妳這個懶散的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要賴在那裡\N動一動，起來幹活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹嘛脾氣那麼大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們賴在那裡\N讓我不能打掃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是輪到我打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾出去曬曬太陽啦\N妳這個瘦竹竿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要躺到什麼時候？\N妳這個笨大姊，走開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，不要礙事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳宇森…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是來得剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來還在想這禮拜沒工作的話\N得把牛奶錢省下來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的任務在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個叫岐阜縣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岐阜縣？是哪個國家？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太沒用了\N這樣也叫貼身保鑣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是貼身保鑣\N不是登山夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那麼斤斤計較
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背著淑女的行李前進\N可是英國紳士的教養
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是道地的美國人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我會另外跟妳申請費用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再開玩笑了，多雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“失落的古墳”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原住民遺留下來的夢幻之墓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是一座山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有外表看起來像一座山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要去那裡幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要冒著\N被讀仙社發現的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是英國的重要機密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要像平常一樣\N保護我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(歡迎來到古墳之鄉)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人很喜歡趕流行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺跡就在附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡還在調查不是嗎？\N不會讓一般人進去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字叫\N愛麗絲.愛麗絲.阿奎特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通稱AAA\N是前大英博物館的考古學者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天前經由衛星確認\N她從成田機場入境了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，好像掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然她是個考古學者\N所以是因為遺跡而來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們用衛星追到這附近\N結果在山林裡追丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附帶一點\N她也是重度的溫泉狂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們能在這一帶埋伏\N並幫我們找到她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這附近旅館很多耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次“吳”也會一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協助你們調查鎮上的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-請多指教\N-對方是一個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，還有一個貼身保鑣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我也不知道啊\N因為四年前沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烘焙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳該不會是來泡溫泉的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能，再怎麼樣\N我也不會公私不分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，泡泡溫泉也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正潛入是晚上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三人是妳的徒弟嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，瞧妳跩的，真臭屁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不收徒弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢\N名義上掛的是貼身保鑣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，幾乎等於是\N賴在我家的食客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不會覺得煩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在學校只要有人靠近妳\N妳都會嫌煩叫他走開的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住了半年以上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳居然沒把他們趕出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前跟操紙師一起不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是三人組\N應該不是同一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是那傢伙，我也不會放過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為護衛妳是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你女兒的養育費\N好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人手上有什麼書？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜可能是\N“不該靠近的血之書”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是英國的超重要書籍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得之前是\N“脈搏跳動肉之書”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和“提升思考之書”對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關聯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是巧合而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表很年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，你們在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-堇川\N-堇川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐，等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒路可走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別說話，你看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追過來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看過的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是普通的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛，因為有點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡是誰在看家？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底在追誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下再跟妳說\N妳在外面等著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-現在就說\N-老師，很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活費快跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把它毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師，對不起\N待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊繩子過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有這個辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是讀仙社的操紙師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把紙片扔掉，轉過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬，一口氣上喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不會開槍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姊，蜜姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想爭取點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是也不必那麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不會開槍不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不干涉你的思想信念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是任務請徹底完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有水嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是喔，是瑪姬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是站在妳這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫妳帶路，跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溼氣很重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是這樣才沒有朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男的\N知道怎麼跟操紙師作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經報警了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，那兩人都可以殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜雪兒跟瑪姬都不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然，姊姊他們比我強多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該先知會我一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了妳會生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都這麼危險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，姊姊們會保護我\N所以很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我要繼續工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈姊就…回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了我會擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問，你知不知道\N我姊姊和妹妹在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我認識的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不認識，我只是偶然路過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-偶然？\N-快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛洗一洗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，我還沒看到你的臉\N也不知道你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜姊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古人製作的保險箱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會發光？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是想把水煮溫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹嘛脫衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真笨\N穿著衣服下去會溼掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要催我\N要按照順序來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古人把神像藏在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓其他種族搶去\N玷污了神像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄錯順序的話，機關會啟動\N讓人掉到地下水脈裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才得這麼急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一被調查團隨便亂搞\N一切就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面藏著什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機密是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開啟全新世界的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了\N接著離開這裡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒極了\N這才是最棒的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是普通的溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有如絲綢般的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一度都不會改變的適溫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中所包含的礦物成分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓體溫上升\N活化腦部的運作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是奇蹟的溫泉\N一切文化的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便妳說，快起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我享受一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在池裡不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把寶物交出來\N這次一定會打到你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把小孩跟圈外人捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點，應該還有另一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊，艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也不准動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲，快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們把紙扔進溫泉裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是，把武器扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操紙師？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我的運氣不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的貼身保鑣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是要鑰匙還是什麼\N全部拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-鑰匙？\N-多雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧，愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙在背包裡\N所以饒她一命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混帳！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是已經說要投降了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大概是我見過的\N最強操紙師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻也是最無恥的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我沒有履行契約
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下祠堂邊的石頭按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下的溫泉會噴出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被開除了\N回去你女兒身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是上次襲擊我們的傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死就快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是愛麗絲送你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真的很遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.11,0:21:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，報酬會給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，只有一半
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀仙社並不小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀仙社？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:25.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍藏的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:31.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是凋零散落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:35.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有和你的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:41.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深烙在我心深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:47.48,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸轉涼的海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:53.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人嬉戲的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:57.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你曬得黝黑的皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:03.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融化在西沉的夕陽裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.23,0:23:08.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願牽著的手永不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:16.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣長大成人該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:23.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陽光下追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:27.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:34.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到戀情結束的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:38.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互依偎
